name: Inspiration Dawning 2
description: ‘Inspiration Dawning 2', 2021 is my second-ever NFT. I feel so fortunate when my muse comes around. This piece is a part of my digital abstract series. Like all of them, my digital abstracts begin life as photographs and I go from there, and I believe these digital abstracts to be photographs. File: 9.3 MB PNG, 3234 × 2158.
